<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <!-- Basic metadata for SEO and responsive design -->
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Name – Civil Engineering Portfolio</title>

  <!-- Google Fonts for clean, professional typography -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- CSS Styles -->
  <style>
    /* Reset some default browser styles */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    /* Body styling */
    body {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f9f9f9; /* light background for modern feel */
    }

    /* Header and navigation */
    header {
      background-color: #1f2937; /* dark gray-blue for professional look */
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px 0;
      position: sticky; /* keeps navbar at top */
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-around;
      align-items: center;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      background-color: #374151;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    /* Main sections styling */
    section {
      padding: 80px 20px;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #1f2937;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #4b5563; /* subtle underline for modern look */
      display: inline-block;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
    }

    section p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Homepage / Hero Section */
    #home {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 120px 20px;
      background-color: #e5e7eb; /* subtle light gray background */
    }

    #home h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #111827;
    }

    #home p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #374151;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* About Me Section */
    #about img {
      max-width: 200px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Skills Section */
    .skills-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .skill {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .skill:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    /* Projects Section */
    .projects-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .project {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .project h3 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #1f2937;
    }

    .project p {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Career Goals Section */
    #goals ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    /* Contact Section */
    #contact form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    #contact input, #contact textarea {
      padding: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      font-size: 1rem;
      width: 100%;
    }

    #contact button {
      padding: 12px;
      background-color: #1f2937;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    #contact button:hover {
      background-color: #374151;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #1f2937;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    /* Responsive Typography */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      #home h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      section h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
    }

    /* Smooth scrolling for nav links */
    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Header with navigation -->
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="#home">Home</a>
      <a href="#about">About Me</a>
      <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
      <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
      <a href="#goals">Career Goals</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- Homepage / Hero Section -->
  <section id="home">
    <h1>Civil Engineering Student Focused on Structural Design and Real-World Engineering Challenges</h1>
    <p>Welcome to my professional portfolio. I am a first-year student at the University of New Haven with a passion for structural engineering, problem-solving, and building sustainable, resilient structures.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- About Me Section -->
  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <!-- Add your professional photo here -->
    <img src="your-photo.jpg" alt="Your Name">
    <p>My interest in civil engineering began in high school when I took an introductory engineering class that explored how structures and infrastructure are designed. That experience sparked my curiosity about how engineers create safe and efficient buildings and bridges. Outside of academics, I enjoy working out and played football all four years of high school, which taught me teamwork, discipline, and perseverance.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Skills Section -->
  <section id="skills">
    <h2>Skills & Competencies</h2>
    <div class="skills-container">
      <div class="skill">
        <h3>Mathematics</h3>
        <p>Building analytical foundations for engineering calculations and structural analysis.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill">
        <h3>Physics</h3>
        <p>Applying mechanics principles to understand forces and behaviors in structures.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill">
        <h3>CAD / Design Software</h3>
        <p>Learning computer-aided design tools for modeling and planning engineering structures.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill">
        <h3>Programming</h3>
        <p>Exploring coding for data analysis and engineering problem solving.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill">
        <h3>Engineering Design</h3>
        <p>Developing solutions that balance safety, efficiency, and practicality.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill">
        <h3>Problem Solving & Teamwork</h3>
        <p>Collaborating with peers and approaching complex challenges with structured thinking.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Projects Section -->
  <section id="projects">
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <div class="projects-container">
      <div class="project">
        <h3>Design Sprint Winner – Dormitory Heat Overload Solution</h3>
        <p><strong>Organization:</strong> University of New Haven</p>
        <p>Analyzed heat buildup in dorms and proposed practical, energy-efficient solutions.</p>
        <p>Skills: Engineering design, problem solving, team collaboration, presenting technical ideas.</p>
        <p>Outcome: Selected as the winning solution, demonstrating creativity and real-world problem-solving.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- You can add more projects here as you complete them -->
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Career Goals Section -->
  <section id="goals">
    <h2>Career Goals</h2>
    <p>As I continue my studies, I aim to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Work on large structural and construction projects, contributing to safe and innovative buildings.</li>
      <li>Develop sustainable and resilient structures that serve communities for generations.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section id="contact">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>I am always interested in learning opportunities, research collaborations, and internships related to civil and structural engineering. Please reach out using the form below or connect via email or LinkedIn.</p>

    <!-- Simple contact form -->
    <form action="mailto:your-email@example.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain">
      <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
      <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
      <textarea name="message" rows="6" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
      <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
    </form>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:your-email@example.com">your-email@example.com</a></p>
    <p>LinkedIn: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/yourprofile" target="_blank">linkedin.com/in/yourprofile</a></p>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    &copy; 2026 Your Name. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
